name: Sugar Marshmallow Bangle
description:
A handmade clay bangle made to look like a rope of marshmallow, which has been glittered with opalescent glitter. 

Available in 3 standard sizes, but can be custom fit to your hand. Please email contact@dollydarling with the diameter you require.

For best fit, measure the diameter of another bangle that you own to compare sizes. To measure by circumference, put your thumb & little finger together, & measure around the hand over the knuckles. 

Sizes:-
Small - 6.5cm diameter (8 inch circumference approx)
Medium - 7cm diameter (9 inch circumference approx)
Large - 8cm diameter (10 inch circumference approx)

If you are between sizes, I recommend sizing up, or getting a custom fit.
